title: Harbin–Yichun high-speed railway
text:
The Harbin–Yichun high-speed railway is a <a href="high-speed%20railway">high-speed railway</a> line in <a href="Heilongjiang">Heilongjiang</a>, <a href="China">China</a>.
Route.
The line is long and has a maximum speed limit of . It will reduce the travel time between <a href="Harbin">Harbin</a> and <a href="Yichun%2C%20Heilongjiang">Yichun</a> from over seven hours to 100 minutes. Construction started on May 13, 2021.
